# Dead-weight local mirrors of GHL/CDN media. Every page references these images
# by absolute https:// URL (verified: zero local-path references), so browsers
# fetch them from the real CDN — the local copies are never served and only bloat
# the deploy. Runtime image optimisation of the CDN-hosted images is deferred to
# the hydration-focused rebuild (see SEO-PROGRESS.md), since those images live in
# the Nuxt data payload.
assets.cdn.filesafe.space/
storage.googleapis.com/
images.squarespace-cdn.com/
